'''Pol Secura''' was a [[Gender/Legends|male]] [[Twi'lek/Legends|Twi'lek]] who was the uncle of [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knight]] [[Aayla Secura/Legends|Aayla Secura]] and [[Nat Secura]] and the brother of [[Lon Secura]]. He was also a member of the [[Twi'lek Ruling Council]] and the [[Clan Chief]] of [[Clan Secura]].

==Biography==
[[File:PSdead.jpg|thumb|left|180px|Secura's death]]
When Aayla's father died, Pol took the young [[Twi'lek/Legends|Twi'lek]] girl but he soon sold her to the local [[Hutt/Legends|Hutt]], pretending she would be safe with him. Later, when he discovered the amount of money that he could make by [[Smuggler/Legends|smuggling]], he started smuggling protected animals. But his illegal activities were soon discovered by the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] and the [[Jedi Council/Legends|Jedi Council]] sent [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Tholme/Legends|Tholme]] and his [[Padawan/Legends|Padawan]] [[Quinlan Vos/Legends|Quinlan Vos]] to investigate the case. Pol denied he had anything to do with the smuggling but when a [[Wampa/Legends|wampa]] he had sold to the local Hutt earlier broke out, things came to light. To show his regret, he agreed to let Aayla be trained as a Jedi.

Ten years later, Pol was approached by [[Chom Frey Kaa]]. After Kaa invented [[glitteryll]], he needed an experienced smuggler to bring this drug into the black market. He promised to protect Pol from his fate and Pol agreed to help Kaa. His illegal activities were discovered by the Jedi again and this time they sent Quinlan with his new Padawan, Aayla. Pol did not want to kill the Jedi so he erased their memory with glitteryll. Aayla became a dancer in his estate and Quinlan was taken to [[Nar Shaddaa/Legends|Nar Shaddaa]]. Though Quinlan's memory was erased he managed to retrieve much of it and following these memories he came back to Pol, asking for his Padawan. Aayla was unable to recognize Quinlan, who [[Torture/Legends|tortured]] Pol with [[Force lightning/Legends|Force lightning]] to make him confess. Aayla wanted to protect Pol and used [[Telekinesis/Legends|Force Push]] to blow both Quinlan and Pol off the balcony. Quinlan was the only one to survive.

